Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.27,0:00:05.15,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Awesome!\N- There's snow everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.15,0:00:06.90,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.90,0:00:08.44,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's nice and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.65,0:00:11.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't these outfits a bit loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:13.20,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Even for rentals.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:17.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now. We shouldn't\Nlet this trip go to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:19.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,All together now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:21.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:30.25,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, I'm actually better at snowboarding.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:32.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act so cocky—you're Haruta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:35.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:37.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep my legs spread...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.09,0:00:39.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't skied since middle\Nschool. It's not so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.26,0:00:41.97,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.97,0:00:43.98,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ho, ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.39,0:00:48.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, not bad, Minori-chan.\NYou're a natural athlete.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.19,0:00:51.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:53.69,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty good yourself, Amin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.69,0:00:55.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I'm average.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:00:56.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:00:57.82,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.82,0:00:59.74,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:01.95,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn sideways, against the slope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:03.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sideways?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:04.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:07.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:08.50,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it! Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:10.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.13,0:01:15.97,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,(My Silky Love)\NEvery time I think of you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.13,0:01:15.97,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,MY SILKY LOVE nijuu yojikan zutto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:19.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,(My Silky Love)\Nfor 24 hours straight,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:19.39,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,MY SILKY LOVE kimino koto omoutabi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:22.89,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,(My Silky Love)\NIt only makes me feel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:22.89,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,MY SILKY LOVE modokashii kono kimochi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.89,0:01:26.98,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,(My Silky Love)\Nthat much more impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.89,0:01:26.98,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,MY SILKY LOVE tada afure kaetteku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:33.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so simple just to say I love you.\NBut when you come close to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:33.94,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,sukito ieba kantan nanoni\Nkimiga maeni kichauto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.94,0:01:40.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,my own emotions go awry\Nand get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.94,0:01:40.91,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,kyaraga sobie watashino\Nkoto wo jamashiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:48.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I can bring myself to do anything.\NThat's who I'm supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:48.46,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,itsumonaraba tsuyoki de ikeru\Nsonna seikakunanoni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.62,0:01:54.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But I just can't break this\Nwall down no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.62,0:01:54.80,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,donna ganbatte mitemo kabewa kuzusenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:58.38,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Please understand these feelings for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:58.38,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,sasshite hoshii kono kimoch iwo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:01.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why these gazes of mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:01.93,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,dakara watashi wa itsumo kimini
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:05.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,they tell my love for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:05.52,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,daisuki dayoto okuru shisen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:09.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Now gather up my courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:09.52,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,saidaino yuukide
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:13.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A fragile heart made of silk,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:13.07,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,yabure souna shirukuno haato
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:16.61,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized that by meeting you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:16.61,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,kimini atte kizuita yatto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.61,0:02:22.32,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so clumsy when it comes to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.61,0:02:22.32,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,ainiwa bukiyou dattan datte
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:27.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A forgotten scar left in my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:27.04,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,wasure kaketa koino kizuato
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:30.58,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,and I suddenly felt it sting deep inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:30.58,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,kyuuni uzuki dashitano kyunto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:35.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to say that I love you someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:35.09,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,itsukawa watashi rashiku sukito iwanakya
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:39.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Or it'll keep making me weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:39.93,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,imayori yowaku nacchauyo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:47.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, don't run me over with a sled...\NWhy're you even on one, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:50.69,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't Help Myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:51.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not by choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:53.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You can't ski?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:56.11,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the smug look?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:03:01.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was the only one,\Nbut you can't ski either!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:03.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,End of the world, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:06.45,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, skiing is so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:10.50,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point in strapping on two\Nlong sticks to glide across snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:16.88,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree with you, but you could\Nask Kitamura to teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:19.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What can he teach me if I'm on a sled?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:22.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't {\i1}you{\i0} go ask Minorin for lessons?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:24.43,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:27.97,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No point in being independent\Nif you're gonna be so useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:31.14,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey, hey! You can ride \Nthe lift two at a time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna ride with Maruo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.83,0:03:35.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I mind, but shouldn't\Nyou ride with Kashii?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:38.90,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako and I want to take pictures\Nof each other on the lifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:40.15,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:41.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What're they up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:42.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:45.28,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, normally you'd be like,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:48.58,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,"What's with that bimbo who keeps\Nthrowing herself at Kitamura-kun!?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:50.20,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,before going on a rampage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.41,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:53.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen between\Nyou and Kitamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:56.54,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:00.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:01.51,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:03.43,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:05.97,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, maybe you could\Nsay something did...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.43,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:09.14,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:12.35,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I bumped into Kitamura-kun on New Year's\Nand we got something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:15.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we went to a shrine for\Nthe typical New Year's ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:17.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:19.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So something did happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:20.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:25.95,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you were in bed with the flu.\NI couldn't brag while you were suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:28.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I need an excuse, anyway!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:31.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not obligated to tell you\Nevery single thing I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:32.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you getting so mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:33.37,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,My point is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:35.54,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to butt in every time!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:37.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you always interfere!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:39.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a big pain in the ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:41.59,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's being selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:45.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use little tricks because you want\Nto throw yourself at Kitamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:47.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't use any tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:48.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You did! You definitely did!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:50.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:53.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to help our buddy find happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:54.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Haruta?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:55.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.31,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:05:02.69,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but your little tricks are\Nlame and destroy the vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:07.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Like I care if a moron thinks they're lame!\N- Hey, guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:10.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, everyone. Let's all get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:13.45,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our class trip, \Nso let's not fight, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:15.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll settle this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:17.08,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What would that accomplish!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:19.92,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:21.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Could everybody just calm down?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:22.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:25.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:30.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yusaku, are you clueless by nature,\Nor are you doing it on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:31.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you implying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:35.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've got something to say, spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:38.65,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, are you really such\Na simpleton, Maruo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:40.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost oppressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:56.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After a first day like \Nthis, I can forget about
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.26,0:05:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}\Nfinding out how Kushieda feels...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:02.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doubt I'll get the chance to talk\Nto her before the trip's over...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:04.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why so down, Taka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:06.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's acting weird today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:08.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all so gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:11.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:14.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Taka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:15.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:17.14,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come to think of it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:22.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kitamura never mentioned anything\Nabout going to the shrine with Taiga.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:26.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've no idea what any of them are thinking...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:30.20,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Caught you sighing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:31.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ku—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:32.45,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:33.58,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Going to the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:35.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:38.83,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you leave the dining hall by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:41.75,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you keep a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:43.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A...A secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:46.88,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I've actually been waiting\Nfor this chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:48.22,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Same here—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:51.14,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how Noto-kun and\NMaya-chan got into a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:54.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help them make up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:58.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, this is our class trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:01.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd suck if they ended up\Nfighting the whole time, so—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:03.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:05.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:07.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:10.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a good way to solve this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:14.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,There's the issue of Maya-chan wanting to be
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.09,0:07:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,around Kitamura-kun all the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:18.95,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's only half the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:20.87,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:27.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Know why Noto-kun is interfering\Nwith Maya-chan's advances?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:31.97,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because he mistakenly thinks\Nthat Taiga likes Kitamura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:35.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's trying to help her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:36.22,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:39.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure that he's wrong...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:43.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know everything about Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:44.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:46.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:49.44,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I know everything about Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:53.61,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:54.99,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:56.62,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:08:01.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She told me to treasure it because\Nit's really important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:04.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:07.25,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I mean the hair clip, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:08.92,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's no use, Taiga...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:12.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It doesn't matter how hard I try...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:15.58,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to face reality.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:19.92,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kushieda isn't going to accept my feelings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:27.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's pretending that Christmas Eve,\Nmy unrequited love, never happened.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:31.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay in there, Takasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:32.32,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:35.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We're worried about you—really worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:39.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:43.25,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Better make sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:44.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa there, Kitamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:45.62,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:46.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you taking your clothes off!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:49.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be really sick\Nto only take your pants off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:51.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And what're you dangling\Nover Takasu's face!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:54.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh, I can feel some sort of\Ngas about to exit my butt...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:57.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:08:58.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:01.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:09.61,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ku-Kushieda!? As in {\i1}the{\i0} Kushieda!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:11.90,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we know any others?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:14.24,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm talking about Kushieda Minori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:17.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been in love with that\Noddball for over a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:18.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So shoot me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:20.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was rejected on Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She cut me off before I \Ncould tell her how I feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.67,0:09:24.12,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:27.62,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would our Kushieda turn you down?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:28.75,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:29.75,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'd like to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:32.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were a girl, I'd definitely\Ngo out with you, Taka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:35.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, that doesn't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:36.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's settled! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:38.51,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:41.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,To ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:42.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:43.31,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:45.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No sweat, Taka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:47.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is just like Chushingura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:50.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Asano Takumi-no-Kami,\Nand we're the Ako Ronin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:52.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, yep. And Kushieda is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:54.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man, Kira's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:57.24,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kitamura only wants to\Nget even with the girls.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:58.82,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's just using me as an excuse.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:01.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle is joined, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:02.74,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Surrender quietly or...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:03.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:05.75,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Nobody's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:08.08,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And they left the door unlocked...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:09.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:11.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it such a pigsty?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:14.59,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu! Control yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:15.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't clean this up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:18.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I just found a light blue camisole!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:20.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a slightly damp towel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:22.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:24.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, that's a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:26.43,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:28.44,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not how it looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:32.27,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't stand seeing lone socks,\Nso I'm pairing them up...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:40.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd it have to be Tiger!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:47.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:50.71,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're using that to wipe the floor!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:53.38,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Rub-a-dub-dub.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:56.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't dry your hair with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:57.59,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Breathe, Takasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:05.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the door's unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:08.27,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Tiger came back before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:14.98,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:17.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Jeez, did we forget to lock the door?\N- Please, don't make a sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:18.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:19.61,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only favor I'll ever ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:26.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, that felt so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:29.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako, you really love to take baths.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:32.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And Ami-chan, you should seriously\Ntry to get into swimsuit modeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:34.71,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be a huge hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:36.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:39.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not that interested\Nin becoming a celebrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:42.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, where'd Taiga run off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:43.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't she come back before us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:48.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Kushieda, that's body cream.\N- Think she went to the guys' room alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:50.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She could be with Maruo this very moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:52.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,As if. You're imagining things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:55.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can totally see Yusaku walking in
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on her and Takasu-kun \Nleaping in to intervene.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:00.32,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:04.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, no! That would suck if it were true!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:07.37,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,How's Tiger really feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:08.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she after Maruo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:11.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda, do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:15.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Does Tiger's heart belong\Nto Takasu-kun, or Maruo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:18.34,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can't say I know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:20.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to ask Taiga when she gets back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:23.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But she would never tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:26.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, haven't you been sorta quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:27.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:29.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I pushed myself\Ntoo hard on the slopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:31.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:32.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:33.98,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't expect to get any sleep tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.85,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to have some serious girl talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:40.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, Takasu-kun and Tiger\Nshould just hook up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:42.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Then all our problems would be solved, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:46.45,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:49.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And Minori-chan falls silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:52.50,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:54.08,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:55.83,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You heard me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.54,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Minori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:13:00.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,See what happens when you play dumb?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:02.97,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I've said something I shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:04.59,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:06.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stare at each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:07.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Spill the goods, Ami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:09.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:11.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do, Minori-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:12.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:13.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:14.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:17.83,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about how you \Ncut off Takasu-kun as he was
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,trying to tell you his feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:21.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:23.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:25.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:27.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun was going to ask you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:28.74,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:31.62,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know about this, Ami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:35.54,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,How, indeed. What a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:38.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you have to bring this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:41.59,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you won't stop playing dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:46.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you can sit there and\Nsay those things with a straight face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:50.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun is in love with you, not Tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:53.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But you shot him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:57.44,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And now you're acting like you\Nforgot it ever happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:14:00.56,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What with your little \N"friends forever" pitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:02.61,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit here with a straight face?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:04.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you actually see it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:06.74,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how I feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:08.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a mind-reader now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:09.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:11.41,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:14.37,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,None of my business, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:16.25,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:19.42,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So this has nothing to do with guilt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:24.88,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I was convinced that you were\Ninterested in Takasu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:30.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,and you only rejected him out\Nof guilt for a certain someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:32.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:36.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You rejected him because you don't like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:39.85,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sure to let him know that tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:41.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, shouldn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:43.88,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better to drive the \Nlast nail in the coffin
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nrather than let him think there's hope, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.73,0:14:48.99,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Suit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:51.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, maybe I'll go tell him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:51.74,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:53.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Go right ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:59.29,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some mask you're wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:02.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:04.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you, Ami-chan!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:08.51,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our class trip! We shouldn't fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:09.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:11.30,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami-chan, you crossed the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:13.14,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize, then let's drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:23.27,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry Minori-chan, I went too far.\NCould you forget this ever happened, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:32.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Deal. It's all good. Never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:36.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, Tiger still isn't back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:37.16,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.33,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where she went?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:40.50,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maybe we should go look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:42.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Kushieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:52.22,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure we weren't\Nsupposed to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:54.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Kushieda sure was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:58.18,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I the only one who doesn't get\Nwhat they were arguing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:16:00.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,How is Ami-chan involved in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:02.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Taka-chan! What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:04.48,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'd like to know that, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:05.61,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:08.44,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We saw nothing, we heard nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:12.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seriously...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:15.62,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This sucks...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:24.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:28.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I was tired, so I'm taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:34.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:39.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be my fault that\NMinori-chan rejected you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:43.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,A while back, I said something spiteful to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NMinori-chan when you weren't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:48.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:50.82,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:53.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:58.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, she and I got into a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:01.54,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It just pissed me off to see her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:05.71,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, she refuses to be honest with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:12.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep pushing and pushing, but she\Nrefuses to tell me how she truly feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:14.43,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,And that infuriates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:17.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you for being an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:19.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:22.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate myself for being an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:26.39,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,My guilt made me screw everything \Nup again and again,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and now here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:32.15,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Dumb-chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:33.94,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:39.53,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:40.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:43.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times are you going\Nto hit me with that sled!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:44.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:47.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, I'm trying to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:50.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll buy you ice cream when\Nwe get back to the lodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:52.17,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw that! It's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:55.38,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for not stopping, Amin...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:56.97,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:17:59.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That was on purpose, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:18:00.60,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It had to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:03.18,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:04.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,We just couldn't stop the sled—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:06.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You were targeting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.19,0:18:09.36,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you're still mad about what\Nhappened yesterday, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:12.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You came crashing in just because\NI was talking with Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:16.49,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:18.99,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean when you tried\Nto pick a fight with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:22.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- I let it go, but you want to rehash it!?\N- Hey, that's enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:24.95,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You let it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:27.08,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been ignoring me all morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:30.21,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That superior attitude pisses me off,\NLittle Miss Musclehead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:32.04,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What superior attitude!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:35.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to be the bigger person,\Nbut you keep crossing the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:38.22,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:43.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you hit my face, you freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:44.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you're an actress!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:45.43,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:48.35,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I hated you the second I laid eyes on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:50.69,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- You pissed me off!\N- Yikes, that doesn't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:52.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh, really? So what!?\N- They going at it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:55.23,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- I don't give a damn if you hate me!\N- Fools! Don't just stand there. Stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:57.28,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Minorin!\N- I hate you! I hate you! I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:18:58.65,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:18:59.61,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you calm down?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:10.00,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:11.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:12.46,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything okay!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:13.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell are you all doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:15.42,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:16.09,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:17.42,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:20.01,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:26.14,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:31.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.44,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:35.11,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Ami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:36.73,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,- Kushieda, what's wrong with you!?\N- Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:38.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:40.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:42.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:45.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Taiga had vanished.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:52.71,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,The lodge has staff out searching.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:55.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,If they can't find her, \Nthey'll call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:58.38,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:00.97,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull yourself together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:02.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll definitely find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:03.22,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:05.18,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Taiga...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:06.68,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a blizzard out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:08.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:09.18,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the getup?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:11.64,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going out to look for her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:14.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid? You'll end up\Nstranded out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:16.11,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But...I can't just sit here and wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:17.65,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:21.15,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just check the area where we were,\Nand then I'll come straight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:22.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:23.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:25.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:27.41,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:28.70,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Count me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:29.62,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:31.79,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Let Teach know we headed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:32.58,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:35.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:37.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:39.51,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun! Kitamura-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:40.96,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:44.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,There are signs that she\Nslipped down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:46.93,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:50.43,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:51.52,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:53.06,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.10,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:56.77,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and get some help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:58.69,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:00.32,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:12.83,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I did it again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:15.76,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I left her all alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.28,0:21:19.67,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She was right next to me,\Nand I didn't even notice...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:23.63,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:25.55,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stupid klutz...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:29.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time I catch you, I'll never let you go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:40.07,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:42.57,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:44.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:45.24,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:46.95,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.45,0:21:49.91,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I fell...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:52.66,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:02.13,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.09,0:22:05.97,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kitamura-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.97,0:22:07.84,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:10.34,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were Ryuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.22,0:22:17.19,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Ryuji's always the one\Nwho comes to my rescue...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.19,0:22:19.31,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:22.02,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:26.86,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Kitamura-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.86,0:22:32.03,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not doing your job as the\NPatron Saint of Broken Hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.24,0:22:37.38,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,My wishes haven't come true...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:42.34,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Erase these feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.17,0:22:45.59,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Make me strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.63,0:22:48.72,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:51.05,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.47,0:22:53.14,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,from loving...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.81,0:22:55.22,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.02,0:23:03.90,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I ate the orange today but cried\Nbecause it was still too sour.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.02,0:23:03.90,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,orenji kyoumo tabete mitakedo\Nmada suppakute naita
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.90,0:23:07.40,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It reminded too much of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.90,0:23:07.40,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,watashi mitaide nokosenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:09.78,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,so I finished the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.40,0:23:09.78,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,zenbu tabeta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.78,0:23:16.41,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you. It's bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.78,0:23:16.41,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,sukidayo suppai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:24.80,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me cry. I love you. I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:24.80,LyricsromajiBD,,0000,0000,0000,,nakeruyo sukidayo sukidayo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:35.01,ImagetextBD,,0000,0000,0000,,When You're Around
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:26.59,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga loves me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.59,0:23:28.38,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me, of all people?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.38,0:23:31.34,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, super thick stud!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.34,0:23:34.26,DefaultBD,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'd say that's a stretch.
